[106731244006584345247,101000792334172783764,The husband and wife team who run the pub make you feel as if you belong there, firstly by having a photographic memory of your face and pairing that with the usual drink, and secondly by remembering that you have been tramping the hills above Tillicoultry and might be a tad thirsty. I would recommend this pub to you - particularly if you like real ales, but also if you like real Guinness as I do.]
